text: pitabrakd nasa a l laoh chea anakdoeng nouv damnoeng nei thngai barlok ning kar banhchouh tukaphlieng . haey trong chea anakdoeng nouv ei v del mean knong sbaun . haey kmean bokkol na mneak doeng tha tae avei delke nung ttuol ban now thngaisaek laey . haeyka kmean bokkol na mneak doeng tha tae ke nung slab now leu tukdei na der . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh mha doeng mha chruotachreab
